# log8-office — License & Usage Notice

**log8-office** is a fork of [Star Office UI](https://github.com/ringhyacinth/Star-Office-UI),
originally co-created by **Ring Hyacinth** and **Simon Lee**. In this fork **all art
assets have been replaced with original, openly-licensed artwork** so the whole
project — code *and* art — is free for any use, including commercial use.

