## 2. Art Assets License (CC0 1.0 — Public Domain)

All art assets in this fork — character sprites, scene backgrounds, furniture,
plants, posters, coffee machine, server room, animations, button skins, app
icons, and the README cover images — are **original work created for log8-office**
and are released under **[Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal](https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/)**
(public domain dedication).

You may use, copy, modify, and redistribute them for **any purpose, including
commercial use, with no attribution required** (attribution is always welcome).

Every art asset is generated by the scripts in [`assets-gen/`](assets-gen/) from
the `pixelkit` toolkit. To re-skin the office with your own style, edit the
palette/generators and run them again — no external art packs needed.

> Note: the upstream Star Office UI art was licensed for **non-commercial** use
> only and is **not** included here — it has been fully replaced by the CC0
> assets described above. No third-party art (including the previously-bundled
> LimeZu guest sprites) remains in this repository.

---

## 3. Fonts

All pixel fonts shipped here — under `frontend/fonts/` and
`desktop-pet/src/ark-pixel-zh_cn.woff2` — are **Ark Pixel Font**
(https://github.com/TakWolf/ark-pixel-font), licensed under the
**SIL Open Font License 1.1** (see `frontend/fonts/OFL.txt`). Keep the OFL notice
when redistributing the fonts. No other third-party font is bundled.
